            },
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The durnolith unleashes a roar of pain and fury. The durnolith attempts a single Intimidation check to Demoralize all living creatures within 60 feet that can hear the durnolith. Roll once and apply the results to all creatures. Each creature is then temporarily immune for 1 minute.",
            "traits": [
              {
                "alternate_link": {
                  "alternate_type": "legacy",
